##format

Push.send({from: 'tester',
		   title: 'testing notifications!',
		   text: 'can you see me ?', 	
		   query: {userId: 'MTXsQhyNCe8DpMJ4N'}
		   });

the parameter userId is the addressee.

thats it.


****************************************
To test. run app normally on device.
->then run 'meteor shell'  from project directory.
->then run above command i.e. Push.send  
Note: commands run on meteor shell are just running on the server. good for debugging.